From skolenik at gmail.com  Wed May 18 17:33:49 2016
From: skolenik at gmail.com (Stas Kolenikov)
Date: Wed, 18 May 2016 10:33:49 -0500
Subject: [R-sig-teaching] Teaching R in high school and college science
 and math courses
In-Reply-To: <CABdHhvG9ZpxW3ObKXJ=HfWC846RzTHTJHF5LsD1wqLmoc0H1Mw@mail.gmail.com>
References: <20160517221750.GA50218@lilly.csoft.net>
