Use the t-parametrized form from e.g.,
http://mathworld.wolfram.com/FoliumofDescartes.html

t <- seq(-50, 50, by=0.01)
x <- 3*t/(1+t^3)
y <- 3*t^2/(1+t^3)
plot(x, y, xlim=c(-5, 5), ylim=c(-5, 5), type="l")

(I'm limiting the plot to avoid the huge values that occur near t=-1)

MW

